{"tid":2070791,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"拾年舖面變文宣 x Adella Beaute","createTime":"2020-06-19T11:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T02:34:40.000Z","uid":113263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9850ee29194755567c411904b2cd0a22a7ba907f","tid":2070791,"uid":113263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNsDN71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNsDN71.jpg&h=2b76c0c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舖面變文宣嚟到第四間舖頭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！今次嘅合作對象就喺位於<span style=\"color: red;\">旺角嘅美容鋪「Adella Beaute」</span>，屬於美容、健康產品及個人護理嘅良心小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJJSSy3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJJSSy3.png&h=d35ed2f9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「Adella Beaute」由運動一開始已經表態，默默為香港付出一分綿力。<br />\n過去一年發生種種令香港人感到憤恨及不公義嘅事，「Adella Beaute」良心小店想藉拾年「舖面變文宣」活動去提醒大家<span style=\"color: red;\">千萬唔好忘記一直辛辛苦苦爭取嘅民主自由</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">用舖面變文宣嘅力量去發聲</span>，同時亦希望各個黃店彷效，將香港人嘅聲音帶到每一個角落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">「每個人付出少少就可以聚沙成塔」</span></span><br />\n～Unity is strength～<br />\n『香港係屬於我哋嘅家園，請大家唔好放棄香港，繼續守護住我地嘅屋企！』<br />\n我哋誠徵各路手足為舖變文宣創作，一齊令文宣遍地開花。<br />\n創作救港文藝復興，振興黃色經濟圈，建立香港真正嘅本土資產階級<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>設計圖</em></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H9yzmsz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH9yzmsz.png&h=afe6fe5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xmVxSzf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxmVxSzf.jpg&h=73da32ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>設計SIZE圖</strong></em><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zer5s7F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzer5s7F.png&h=2a371c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdJfQk1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdJfQk1.jpg&h=c8fa0ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>實景圖</em></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mi7GsO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mi7GsO.png&h=9523869c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nsNoZeu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnsNoZeu.png&h=2e573dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議主題：<span style=\"color: red;\">勿忘抗爭</span><br />\n建議風格：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">淺粉紅/淺色為主<br />\n可以有花嘅元素<br />\n以圖案為主</span> <br />\n截稿日期：<span style=\"color: red;\">5/7/2020 23:59</span><br />\n（<span style=\"color: red;\">有興趣請先</span>於telegram聯絡<span style=\"color: red;\">@sapnin2019</span> 或拾年 <span style=\"color: red;\">Sap Nin Facebook</span>，然後跟據店舖及設計者風格作出配合，再設計舖面，以減少浪費設計及資源等問題。）<br />\n評審時間：6/7/2020 <br />\n作品要求：  需附合舖面尺寸限制<br />\n<br />\n*投稿以AI檔案為主，其他檔案亦可。    <br />\n投稿人必須確保其作品為原創作品並持有其所有權限。 <br />\n選中作品展覽於合作商舖「Adella Beaute」店舖門面的外牆上。   <br />\n部分作品亦會展覽於店舖外或透過「拾年」telegram上作宣傳之用。  <br />\n結果將會在於「拾年」telegram channel公佈。<br />\n----------------------------------------------------<br />\n光復香港 時代革命🇭🇰🇭🇰<br />\nFollow 拾年<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sapnin2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsapnin2019%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=6afe7a54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sapnin2019/</a><br />\nInstagram：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/sap_nin?igshid=12o7m9k9o4st5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsap_nin%3Figshid%3D12o7m9k9o4st5&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=f7c804bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/sap_nin?igshid=12o7m9k9o4st5</a><br />\n拾年Telegram：<a href=\"https://t.me/sapnin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsapnin&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=e4832520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sapnin</a><br />\n----------------------------------------------------<br />\nAdella Beaute<br />\nIG@adella.beaute<br />\nFB@Adella Beaute"},{"pid":"f4076e9c7b0082335d7afb1e816f4ceea97378ff","tid":2070791,"uid":113263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:06:28.000Z","msg":"舖面變文宣第4次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3737067af04cca011e10eafbfb90109f5c954b0e","tid":2070791,"uid":113263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"我哋要話比大家聽<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">越係打壓越要反抗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab58845e8308e1d42003baeaf11b4458bd9c39c7","tid":2070791,"uid":113263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:10:18.000Z","msg":"唔可以就咁比人扼殺咗我哋表達言論自由嘅權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4794b0fa3e119e552580ae759932e9f4008d37","tid":2070791,"uid":113263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:10:43.000Z","msg":"創作救港，文藝復興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2055f90a35424bb6c8edda7112266a718da242","tid":2070791,"uid":113263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:11:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kil